#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.2"
msgid "3. Āyācanavagga"
msgstr "3. Appeals"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Nirodhadhammasutta"
msgstr "34. Liable To Cease"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.34:1.2"
msgid "Āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn23.34:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato "
"dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’"
"ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo."
msgstr ""
"“Rādha, you should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for "
"whatever is liable to cease."

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.2"
msgid "Ko ca, rādha, nirodhadhammo?"
msgstr "And what is liable to cease?"

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Form is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, any "
"desire and greed for it."

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.4"
msgid "vedanā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe …"
msgstr "Feeling …"

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.5"
msgid "saññā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.6"
msgid "saṅkhārā nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn23.34:2.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Consciousness is liable to cease. You should give up any desire, any greed, "
"any desire and greed for it."

#. VAR: ti → bj potthake pana imasmiṃ vagge chattiṃsa suttāni vibhattāni ekekaṃ suttaṃ tīṇi tīṇi katvā, evaṃ
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.8"
msgid ""
"yo kho, rādha, nirodhadhammo; tatra te chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, "
"chandarāgo pahātabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"You should give up any desire, any greed, any desire and greed for whatever "
"is liable to cease.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.34:2.9"
msgid "Āyācanavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.200"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.1"
msgid "Māro ca māradhammo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.2"
msgid "Aniccena apare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.3"
msgid "Dukkhena ca duve vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.4"
msgid "Anattena tatheva ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.5"
msgid "Khayavayasamudayaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn23.34:3.6"
msgid "Nirodhadhammena dvādasāti."
msgstr ""
